channel.title: Portals
channel.description: k so theres a portal. how do i change where it tele's you to?

item.title: Portals
item.dc:creator: @combat_evil1 combat evil1
item.description:
@combat_evil1 wrote:

go in your server and then find a currently working portal, and get the object id of it. then go into your client.java and search for it until you see something like this

if(objectID == 7272) { toX = 3233; toY = 9315; heightLevel = 0; }

and then add this

if(objectID == ####) { toX = XXXX; toY = YYYY; heightLevel = 0; }

replace #### with the object id of the portal and then replace XXXX with X cord and replace YYYY with Y cord. save and then compile.
